description: Triangle T(n,k) of number of strongly connected digraphs on n unlabeled nodes and with k arcs, k=0,1,..,n*(n-1).
example: [1],[0,0,1],[0,0,0,1,2,1,1],[0,0,0,0,1,4,16,22,22,11,5,1,1],...; Number of strongly connected digraphs on 3 unlabeled nodes is 5=1+2+1+1.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Goran Kilibarda, Sep 14 2000
